      "body": "Dear Alex,\n\nI hope this email finds you well. I am reaching out to confirm my attendance at the upcoming \"Healing Together\" support group session. I appreciate the opportunity to participate and connect with others in a similar situation.\n\nThank you for organizing this group and providing a safe space for open discussions and mutual support. Please let me know if there are any materials or specific details I should prepare before the session.\n\nLooking forward to hearing from you!\n\nBest regards,  \nJane Doe  \n"
